f members often are available for childcare.  If you would like to plan an adults only activity during your stay, just ask and we can facilitate these arrangements. \r\n', 'Kid\'s Activities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '55-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-24 18:34:12', '2015-03-24 18:34:12', '', '55', 'http://irmr.zendentest.com/55-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
