Galena Summit, providing spectacular views of the Sawtooth Valley.</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>As the IRMR is situated in the Sawtooth Valley 6,600 feet above sea level, we recommend an appropriate cold weather jacket for those cool mornings and crisp evenings.</p>\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"divider\"></div>\r\n		<a class=\"solidbtn\" href=\"files/Directions_Boise_Airport_to_IRMR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Driving Directions - pdf</a><a class=\"solidbtn\" href=\"lodging.php\">View Accommodations</a><a class=\"solidbtn\" href=\"#\">Employment Opportunities</a>\r\n		<div class=\"divider\"></div>', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '98-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-26 18:43:42', '2015-03-26 18:43:42', '', '98', 'http://irmr.zendentest.com/98-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `irmr_posts` VALUES('352', '1', '2015-03-26 19:02:00', '2015-03-26 19:02:00', '<p><strong>The Idaho Rocky Mountain Ranch cabins and lodge rooms are charming and comfortable, with private baths with either stone showers or deep, relaxing bathtubs.</strong></p>\r\n		\r\n		<p>Fourteen cabins, our Family Cabin, the Honeymoon Cabin and four lodge rooms provide you a home away from home in which to relax and prepare for your next adventure. And there are no phones, televisions or radios in the accommodations allowing you to truly unplug.</p>\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"divider\"></div>\r\n		\r\n		<h4>2014 Summer Season, June 13th through September 13th</h4>\r\n		<p>Because the ranch can accommodate only 50 guests at any one time, early reservations are recommended to ensure the dates and choice of accommodations you desire.</p>\r\n		\r\n		<h4>2014 Rates and Inclusions</h4>\r\n		<p>Included in Ranch rates: Breakfast, packed picnic lunch, dinner, mountain bikes, weekly mountain bike clinic with orientation on-Ranch ride, weekly fly casting clinic, and use of the Ranch facility - natural hot springs swimming pool, stocked fishing pond, Salmon River access, 900 scenic acres to roam and explore. Our knowledgeable staff provides concierge service to customize your vacation with the activities you choose.</p>\r\n		\r\n		<p>*Adult and child rates below are per person, per night, based on double occupancy. Cabins accommodate maximum 3 people per Cabin with the third person on a rollaway bed. Families of 4 &mdash; 6 people are accommodated in a duplex cabin (2 connecting Cabins). We will choose the most comfortable accommodations for your party based on your preferences, children’s ages and availability. 15% service charge in lieu of gratuity and applicable taxes are additional.</p>\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"divider\"></div>\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"rates\">\r\n			<h5>June and September</h5>\r\n			<table>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<th><strong>Adult </strong>(age 13+)</th>\r\n					<th><strong>Child </strong>(age 0-12)</th>\r\n					<th><strong>Single Occupant</strong></th>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<th><strong>1-3 Night Rate</strong></th>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Lodge Room</td>\r\n					<td>$204</td>\r\n					<td>N/A</td>\r\n					<td>$297</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Cabin</td>\r\n					<td>$242</td>\r\n					<td>$187</td>\r\n					<td>$374</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Deluxe Cabin</td>\r\n					<td>$281</td>\r\n					<td>$225</td>\r\n					<td>$451</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<th><strong>4+ Night Rate</strong></th>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Lodge Room</td>\r\n					<td>$187</td>\r\n					<td>N/A</td>\r\n					<td>$264</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Cabin</td>\r\n					<td>$226</td>\r\n					<td>$170</td>\r\n					<td>$341</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Deluxe Cabin</td>\r\n					<td>$264</td>\r\n					<td>$209</td>\r\n					<td>$418</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n			</table>\r\n\r\n			<h5>July and August</h5>\r\n			<table>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<th><strong>Adult </strong>(age 13+)</th>\r\n					<th><strong>Child </strong>(age 0-12)</th>\r\n					<th><strong>Single Occupant</strong></th>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<th><strong>1-3 Night Rate</strong></th>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Lodge Room</td>\r\n					<td>$220</td>\r\n					<td>N/A</td>\r\n					<td>$330</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Cabin</td>\r\n					<td>$275</td>\r\n					<td>$220</td>\r\n					<td>$440</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Deluxe Cabin</td>\r\n					<td>$314</td>\r\n					<td>$259</td>\r\n					<td>$517</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<th><strong>4+ Night Rate</strong></th>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n					<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Lodge Room</td>\r\n					<td>$204</td>\r\n					<td>N/A</td>\r\n					<td>$297</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Cabin</td>\r\n					<td>$242</td>\r\n					<td>$187</td>\r\n					<td>$374</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>Deluxe Cabin</td>\r\n					<td>$281</td>\r\n					<td>$225</td>\r\n					<td>$451</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n			</table>\r\n		</div>\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"divider\"></div>\r\n		<h2 class=\"pagetitle\">Reservation Policies\r\n		<a class=\"solidbtn red\" href=\"#\">Request a Reservation</a></h2>\r\n		\r\n		<h4>Rate Details</h4>\r\n		<p>Rates are subject to a 15% service charge, applicable state taxes and change without notice.\r\nThere is a three night minimum stay on reservations made prior to June 1st, unless we are able to fit your request between existing reservations.</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>You may place your name on a waitlist for a shorter stay. Beginning June 1st reservations of any length stay are made.</p>\r\n\r\n		<h4>Reservation Deposits &amp; Payments</h4>\r\n		<p>A 60% deposit is required to confirm all reservations. The balance is due at departure. We accept Visa and Mastercard, personal checks, traveler\'s checks and money orders.</p>\r\n\r\n		<h4>Cancellation Policy</h4>\r\n		<p>Your deposit, less a fee of 10% of the total reservation cost, will be refunded if cancellation is made at least 60 days prior to scheduled arrival. If cancellation or early departure notice is given within 60 days of scheduled arrival, you are responsible for the total reservation cost unless we are able to re-book the accommodations. A refund will be given for rebooked accommodations, less a fee of 10% of the total reservation cost.</p>', 'Rates', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '76-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-26 19:02:00', '2015-03-26 19:02:00', '', '76', 'http://irmr.zendentest.com/76-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `irmr_posts` VALUES('353', '1', '2015-03-26 19:04:52', '2015-03-26 19:04:52', '		<p><strong>The Idaho Rocky Mountain Ranch cabins and lodge rooms are charming and comfortable, with private baths with either stone showers or deep, relaxing bathtubs.</strong></p>\n		\n		<p>Fourteen cabins, our Family Cabin, the Honeymoon Cabin and four lodge rooms provide you a home away from home in which to relax and prepare for your next adventure. And there are no phones, televisions or radios in the accommodations allowing you to truly unplug.</p>\n		\n		<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n		\n		<figure class=\"textimg\">\n			<a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"/img/lodging-cabinmap.jpg\" alt=\"Cabin Map\"></a>\n			<h4>Cabins</h4>\n			<p>Each cabin is well appointed with upgraded (and raved about!) beds and bedding, a rock fireplace, electric heat, private bath and bed(s) for two, either twin beds or a king. A third person can be accommodated on a rollaway bed. Our Cabins are arranged in seven two-cabin duplexes. Four duplexes offer interior connecting doors between the two cabins, to comfortably accommodate families of 4 to 6 people.</p>\n\n			<p>Our Deluxe Family Cabin, for larger families, includes two cabins, each with king bed, and a third room with twin beds. The Deluxe Honeymoon Cabin, with king bed, stands alone. </p>\n			\n			<a class=\"solidbtn red\" href=\"#\">Request a Reservation</a>\n		</figure>\n		\n		<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n		\n		<figure class=\"textimg\">\n			<img class=\"alignright\" src=\"/img/lodging-lodgerooms.jpg\" alt=\"Lodge Rooms\">\n			<h4>Lodge Rooms</h4>\n			<p>Each of our 3 attractively decorated lodge rooms has a queen bed, unique Oakley stone shower and electric heat. These rooms are located off the hallway next to the lodge great room.</p>\n\n			<p>There is a complimentary guest laundry facility on the Ranch, and a courtesy phone, guest laptop computer and wi-fi in the Lodge Great Room.</p>\n			\n			<a class=\"solidbtn red\" href=\"#\">Request a Reservation</a>\n		</figure>\n		\n		<div class=\"divider\"></div>', 'Cabins & Lodge Rooms', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '74-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-03-26 19:04:52', '2015-03-26 19:04:52', '', '74', 'http://irmr.zendentest.com/74-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
