 in the Lodge Great Room.</p>\r\n			\r\n			<a class=\"solidbtn red\" href=\"#\">Request a Reservation</a>\r\n		</figure>\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"divider\"></div>', 'Cabins & Lodge Rooms', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '74-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-26 19:05:50', '2015-03-26 19:05:50', '', '74', 'http://irmr.zendentest.com/74-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
